Natali Vineyards website (www.natalivineyards.com)

Dependencies: Ruby, Rails, MySQL

Setup:
- Install Ruby (v1.8.7), Rails (v2.0.2) and MySQL
- Install required gems (mongrel and will_paginate)
- Create db via db/create.sql
- Optionally load data via db/load_sample_data.sql
- Modify config/mongrel.yml to suit your environment
- Run via mongrel_rails start -C config/mongrel.yml
- Stop via mongrel_rails stop

